#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn48.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.47:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga "
msgstr "5. Old Age "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Tatiyapubbārāmasutta "
msgstr "47. At the Eastern Monastery (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn48.47:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ. "
msgstr "The same setting. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.47:1.2"
msgid "“Katinaṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā khīṇāsavo bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, how many faculties must a mendicant develop and cultivate so that they can declare enlightenment: "

msgctxt "sn48.47:1.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāmī”ti? "
msgstr "‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence”’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn48.47:2.1"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe … "
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.47:2.2"
msgid "“catunnaṃ kho, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā khīṇāsavo bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti: "
msgstr "“A mendicant must develop and cultivate four faculties so that they can declare enlightenment. "

msgctxt "sn48.47:2.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāmīti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn48.47:2.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn48.47:2.5"
msgid "Vīriyindriyassa, satindriyassa, samādhindriyassa, paññindriyassa—"
msgstr "The faculties of energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.47:2.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā khīṇāsavo bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti: "
msgstr "These are the four faculties that a mendicant must develop and cultivate so that they can declare enlightenment: "

msgctxt "sn48.47:2.7"
msgid "‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence”’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.47:2.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
